    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>* dotTV, Pasadena, Calif., a registry for Internet domain names ending in .TV, to the Playa del Rey office of TBWA/Chiat/Day, part of the TBWA Worldwide unit of the Omnicom Group, to handle its first account. Billings were estimated at $15 million to $20 million.</p>
